text: Lotte van Hoek (born 8 August 1991) is a Dutch former professional racing cyclist, who rode professionally between 2015 and 2018, for the Feminine Cycling Team and . ==See also== * List of 2015 UCI Women's Teams and riders ==References== ==External links== * Category:1991 births Category:Living people Category:Dutch female cyclists Category:People from Heusden Category:Sportspeople from North Brabant
